{"tid":240501,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得running man已經唔值得再睇","createTime":"2017-05-12T12:58:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T18:01:44.000Z","uid":85633,"like":78,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"964b028dc261909b7a0562fcaefebd554b78d845","tid":240501,"uid":85633,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T12:58:02.000Z","msg":"本身個節目係好地地 6個咪6個囉<br />\n再唔係開過另一個talkshow節目原班人馬<br />\n一樣咁好睇<br />\n而家<br />\n多左果個梁世贊 同佢阿哥一樣咁黑人憎<br />\n個女仔本身無乜野 而家愈黎愈扮野<br />\n聽到7012變左咩9012<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連原班人馬都好似變晒心咁<br />\n真係對呢個節目好失望 真係心都淡埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我中意左咁耐既節目比佢地一手破壞晒<br />\n呢個rm已經唔係我一開始中意果個rm<br />\n除非果2個人走 唔係我唔會再睇/再支持佢地任何野<br />\n而家連無挑都比姓梁既破壞晒<br />\n最好既2個綜藝已經不復存在<br />\n真係係到同sbs講聲<br />\n求你快d執左rm啦 唔好再害原班人馬喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c128974aaf0eb2e4b2eefc7a9281035883230a0","tid":240501,"uid":68091,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T13:00:10.000Z","msg":"昭旻還可以  定位女臭手 無同智考衝突 但梁世贊太多嗲 好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac44f4a94d8925be93798ae2a3cbf7bf9b31c755","tid":240501,"uid":70205,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T13:01:08.000Z","msg":"韓狗嘢有咩好睇"},{"pid":"da6ccce3bc7c8283e15d80af6af1f465d10a3ba2","tid":240501,"uid":85633,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T13:01:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>昭旻還可以  定位女臭手 無同智考衝突 但梁世贊太多嗲 好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一開始我都幾中意佢拍果d劇<br />\n拍劇還拍劇<br />\n做乜走入黎搞破壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5aab688380cf45a0f4f9894533c738697d32f8e","tid":240501,"uid":2959,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedB